class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/subodh-kant-sahay\/#Address\" title=\"Address\">Address<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/subodh-kant-sahay\/#Signature\" title=\"Signature\">Signature<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/subodh-kant-sahay\/#Career\" title=\"Career\">Career<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/subodh-kant-sahay\/#Controversies\" title=\"Controversies\">Controversies<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/subodh-kant-sahay\/#Attended_a_Fashion_Show_on_Mumbai_Blast_Day\" title=\"Attended a Fashion Show on Mumbai Blast Day\">Attended a Fashion Show on Mumbai Blast Day<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-12\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/subodh-kant-sahay\/#Sahay_Asked_to_Resign_Over_Coal_Scam\" title=\"Sahay Asked to Resign Over Coal Scam\">Sahay Asked to Resign Over Coal Scam<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-13\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/subodh-kant-sahay\/#Compared_PM_Modi_to_Hitler\" title=\"Compared PM Modi to Hitler\">Compared PM Modi to Hitler<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-14\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/subodh-kant-sahay\/#Brief_Details_of_IPCs\" title=\"Brief Details of IPCs\">Brief Details of IPCs<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-15\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/subodh-kant-sahay\/#AssetsProperties\" title=\"Assets\/Properties\">Assets\/Properties<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-16\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/subodh-kant-sahay\/#Movable_Assets\" title=\"Movable Assets\">Movable Assets<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-17\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/subodh-kant-sahay\/#Immovable_Assets\" title=\"Immovable Assets\">Immovable Assets<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-18\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/subodh-kant-sahay\/#Net_Worth\" title=\"Net Worth\">Net Worth<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-19\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/subodh-kant-sahay\/#FactsTrivia\" title=\"Facts\/Trivia\">Facts\/Trivia<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"WikiBiography\"><\/span>Wiki\/Biography<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Subodh Kant Sahay was born on Monday, 11 June 1951 (<strong>age 72 years; as of 2023<\/strong>) in Latehar, Bihar, India. His zodiac sign is Gemini. In 1974, he earned a Bachelor&#8217;s degree in Science at Magadh University in Bihar. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_236453_1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[1]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_236453_1_1\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"http:\/\/chrome-extension\/\/efaidnbmnnnibpcajpcglclefindmkaj\/https:\/\/suvidha.eci.gov.in\/uploads\/counteraffidavit\/2019\/PC\/S27\/8\/S2720190419011559.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Subodh Kant Sahay&#8217;s ECI Document<\/a><\/span><\/span> Later, he earned an LLB degree at Ranchi University, Jharkhand. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_236453_1_2\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[2]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_236453_1_2\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.linkedin.com\/in\/subodh-kant-sahay-9b50b580\/?originalSubdomain=in\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Subodh Kant Sahay&#8217;s LinkedIn Account<\/a><\/span><\/span> Subodh Kant Sahay has been actively involved in social and welfare activities since his college days.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_236505\" style=\"width: 313px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/A-young-Subodh-Kant-Sahay.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-236505\" class=\"size-full wp-image-236505\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/A-young-Subodh-Kant-Sahay.jpg\" alt=\"A young Subodh Kant Sahay\" width=\"303\" height=\"442\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/A-young-Subodh-Kant-Sahay.jpg 303w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/A-young-Subodh-Kant-Sahay-206x300.jpg 206w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 303px) 100vw, 303px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-236505\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">A young Subodh Kant Sahay<\/p><\/div>\n<p>Before entering politics, he was associated with many political movements, including the Non-Aligned Student Youth Organization (NASYO) and the Jai Prakash Movement. He has been part of the Preparatory Committee and World Youth Festival as its General Secretary. He served as the President of Yuva Janata, Janata Party, and Janata Dal.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Physical_Appearance\"><\/span>Physical Appearance<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Height (approx.):<\/strong> 5&#8242; 7&#8243;<\/p>\n<p><strong>Hair Colour: <\/strong>Black<\/p>\n<p><strong>Eye Colour: <\/strong>Black<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-1-1.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-236499\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"Subodh Kant Sahay\" width=\"357\" height=\"541\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-1-1.jpg 357w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-1-1-198x300.jpg 198w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 357px) 100vw, 357px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Family_Caste\"><\/span>Family &amp; Caste<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Subodh Kant Sahay belongs to the Chitraguptavanshi Kayastha community. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_236453_1_3\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[3]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_236453_1_3\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hindustantimes.com\/india\/the-chutney-and-ketchup-minister\/story-IvVfuPzBPbOh4EbXHkmvsJ.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Hindustan Times<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Parents_Siblings\"><\/span><strong>Parents &amp; Siblings<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>His father&#8217;s name is Brij Dev Sahay, and his mother&#8217;s name is Indrani Devi. He has three brothers named Sunil Sahay (politician), Sudhir Sahay, and Tarun Sahay.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_236476\" style=\"width: 287px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-with-Sunil-Kant-Sahay.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-236476\" class=\"wp-image-236476 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-with-Sunil-Kant-Sahay.jpg\" alt=\"Subodh Kant Sahay (left) with Sunil Kant Sahay\" width=\"277\" height=\"210\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-236476\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Subodh Kant Sahay (left) with Sunil Kant Sahay<\/p><\/div>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Wife_Children\"><\/span><strong>Wife &amp; Children<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>On 28 March 1991, Subodh Kant Sahay got married to <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/rekha-sahay\/\">Rekha Sahay<\/a>, a theatre artist. The couple has a daughter named Yashashwini Sahay.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_236482\" style=\"width: 382px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-with-Rekha-Sahay.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-236482\" class=\" wp-image-236482\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-with-Rekha-Sahay.jpg\" alt=\"Subodh Kant Sahay with Rekha Sahay\" width=\"372\" height=\"378\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-with-Rekha-Sahay.jpg 402w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-with-Rekha-Sahay-296x300.jpg 296w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-with-Rekha-Sahay-65x65.jpg 65w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 372px) 100vw, 372px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-236482\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Subodh Kant Sahay with Rekha Sahay<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_236484\" style=\"width: 453px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-with-Rekha-Sahay-and-their-daughter-.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-236484\" class=\" wp-image-236484\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-with-Rekha-Sahay-and-their-daughter-.jpg\" alt=\"Subodh Kant Sahay with Rekha Sahay and their daughter\" width=\"443\" height=\"347\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-with-Rekha-Sahay-and-their-daughter-.jpg 552w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-with-Rekha-Sahay-and-their-daughter--300x235.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 443px) 100vw, 443px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-236484\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Subodh Kant Sahay with Rekha Sahay and their daughter<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"RelationshipsAffairs\"><\/span>Relationships\/Affairs<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>He was in a relationship with <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/rekha-sahay\/\">Rekha Sahay<\/a>\u00a0before marrying her in 1991.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Address\"><\/span>Address<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>His permanent address is E-40, Sector 3, HEC, Dhurwa, Ranchi, 834004.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Signature\"><\/span>Signature<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<div id=\"attachment_236455\" style=\"width: 246px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-Signature.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-236455\" class=\" wp-image-236455\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-Signature.jpg\" alt=\"Subodh Kant Sahay Signature\" width=\"236\" height=\"160\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-236455\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Subodh Kant Sahay Signature<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Career\"><\/span>Career<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>In July 1978, Subodh Kant Sahay was appointed as a Speaker at the Bihar Legislative Assembly, and he served in the position till October 1989. Meanwhile, he was also designated as the President of the Public Accounts Committee for four years, President of the Committee of Privileges for two years, and Vice President of the Library Committee for four years.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_236527\" style=\"width: 343px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-a-member-of-Lok-Sabha-from-Bihar.-in-1989.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-236527\" class=\"wp-image-236527\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-a-member-of-Lok-Sabha-from-Bihar.-in-1989.jpg\" alt=\"Subodh Kant Sahay in New Delhi in 1989\" width=\"333\" height=\"461\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-a-member-of-Lok-Sabha-from-Bihar.-in-1989.jpg 385w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-a-member-of-Lok-Sabha-from-Bihar.-in-1989-217x300.jpg 217w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 333px) 100vw, 333px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-236527\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Subodh Kant Sahay in New Delhi in 1989<\/p><\/div>\n<p>Thereafter, Bihar Janta Party president Satyendra Narayan Sinha asked him to contest the State Legislative Assembly election as a candidate from Hatia, Ranchi. He agreed and won. He became a Member of Parliament in the 9th Lok Sabha from the Ranchi constituency in 1989. He then served as the President of the Committee on Petitions in the Bihar Legislative Assembly for three years.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_236550\" style=\"width: 473px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Ajit-Singh-President-of-Janata-Party-and-Union-Minister-for-Industry-meets-Subodh-Kant-Sahay-Janta-Party-leader-during-a-dinner-hosted-by-him-at-his-residence-in-New-Delhi-during-1990.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-236550\" class=\" wp-image-236550\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Ajit-Singh-President-of-Janata-Party-and-Union-Minister-for-Industry-meets-Subodh-Kant-Sahay-Janta-Party-leader-during-a-dinner-hosted-by-him-at-his-residence-in-New-Delhi-during-1990.jpg\" alt=\"Ajit Singh, President of Janata Party and Union Minister for Industry meets Subodh Kant Sahay, Janta Party leader during a dinner hosted by him at his residence in New Delhi during 1990\" width=\"463\" height=\"362\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Ajit-Singh-President-of-Janata-Party-and-Union-Minister-for-Industry-meets-Subodh-Kant-Sahay-Janta-Party-leader-during-a-dinner-hosted-by-him-at-his-residence-in-New-Delhi-during-1990.jpg 588w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Ajit-Singh-President-of-Janata-Party-and-Union-Minister-for-Industry-meets-Subodh-Kant-Sahay-Janta-Party-leader-during-a-dinner-hosted-by-him-at-his-residence-in-New-Delhi-during-1990-300x235.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 463px) 100vw, 463px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-236550\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ajit Singh, President of Janata Party and Union Minister for Industry meets Subodh Kant Sahay, Janta Party leader during a dinner hosted by him at his residence in New Delhi during 1990<\/p><\/div>\n<p>Subodh Kant Sahay was a Union Minister in the Indian Government from April 1990 to November 1990. He then served as a Union Minister of State for Information and Broadcasting from November 1990 to June 1991. After that, he was appointed as the Secretary of AICC in Uttar Pradesh and Uttarakhand for two years.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_236699\" style=\"width: 307px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/The-logo-of-AICC.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-236699\" class=\" wp-image-236699\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/The-logo-of-AICC.jpg\" alt=\"The logo of AICC\" width=\"297\" height=\"285\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/The-logo-of-AICC.jpg 360w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/The-logo-of-AICC-300x288.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 297px) 100vw, 297px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-236699\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">The logo of AICC<\/p><\/div>\n<p>In the 14th Lok Sabha, he served as a Member of Parliament and was appointed as the Union Minister of State for Food Processing Industries in the First <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/manmohan-singh\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Manmohan Singh<\/a> Cabinet from 2004 to 2009. He was then re-elected to the 15th Lok Sabha in 2009 as a Member of Parliament from the Ranchi constituency.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_236698\" style=\"width: 555px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-while-sworning-as-a-Member-of-Parliament-from-the-Ranchi-constituency-2009.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-236698\" class=\"wp-image-236698 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-while-sworning-as-a-Member-of-Parliament-from-the-Ranchi-constituency-2009.jpg\" alt=\"Subodh Kant Sahay while swearing in as a Member of Parliament from the Ranchi constituency (2009)\" width=\"545\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-while-sworning-as-a-Member-of-Parliament-from-the-Ranchi-constituency-2009.jpg 545w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-while-sworning-as-a-Member-of-Parliament-from-the-Ranchi-constituency-2009-300x220.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 545px) 100vw, 545px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-236698\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Subodh Kant Sahay while swearing in as a Member of Parliament from the Ranchi constituency (2009)<\/p><\/div>\n<p>Subodh Kant Sahay served as the Union Minister for Tourism from 2011 to October 2012.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Controversies\"><\/span>Controversies<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Attended_a_Fashion_Show_on_Mumbai_Blast_Day\"><\/span><strong>Attended a Fashion Show on Mumbai Blast Day<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>In 2011, he attracted controversy when he was pictured attending a fashion show when Mumbai was facing multiple bomb blasts. The Congress party did not comment on the situation and avoided the controversy. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_236453_1_4\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[4]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_236453_1_4\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/economictimes.indiatimes.com\/news\/politics-and-nation\/congress-refuses-to-comment-on-tourism-minister-subodh-kant-sahays-presence-at-fashion-show-on-blast-day\/articleshow\/9240829.cms?from=mdr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">The Economic Times<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_236510\" style=\"width: 372px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-while-attending-a-fashion-show-in-2011.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-236510\" class=\"size-full wp-image-236510\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-while-attending-a-fashion-show-in-2011.jpg\" alt=\"Subodh Kant Sahay while attending a fashion show in 2011\" width=\"362\" height=\"246\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-while-attending-a-fashion-show-in-2011.jpg 362w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-while-attending-a-fashion-show-in-2011-300x204.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 362px) 100vw, 362px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-236510\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Subodh Kant Sahay while attending a fashion show in 2011<\/p><\/div>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Sahay_Asked_to_Resign_Over_Coal_Scam\"><\/span><strong>Sahay Asked to Resign Over Coal Scam<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Former PM <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/manmohan-singh\/\">Manmohan Singh<\/a> asked Sahay to resign from his government job in 2012 due to charges of aiding his brother in a Coal Scam. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_236453_1_5\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[5]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_236453_1_5\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.indiatoday.in\/india\/north\/story\/coalgate-manmohan-singh-subodh-kant-sahai-sonia-gandhi-116480-2012-09-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">India Today<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Compared_PM_Modi_to_Hitler\"><\/span><strong>Compared PM Modi to Hitler<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>In 2022, at a Congress event in Delhi, Subodh Kant Sahay compared Prime Minister <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/narendra-modi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Narendra Modi<\/a> to Hitler, claiming that Modi had surpassed Hitler&#8217;s actions and created a similar organization called &#8216;Khakee.&#8217; Sahay warned Modi to remember this caution and that if he followed Hitler&#8217;s path, he would face a similar fate. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_236453_1_6\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[6]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_236453_1_6\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hindustantimes.com\/india-news\/subodh-kant-sahay-of-congress-says-subodh-modi-will-die-hitler-s-death-101655718419812.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Hindustan Times<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Brief_Details_of_IPCs\"><\/span><strong>Brief Details of IPCs<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>1 charge related to Punishment for criminal intimidation (IPC Section-506)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>1 charge related to Punishment for Being a member of an unlawful assembly (IPC Section-143)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>1 charge related to Punishment of abetment if the act abetted is committed in consequence, and where no express provision is made for its punishment (IPC Section-109)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>1 charge related to Obstructing public servants in the discharge of public functions (IPC Section-186)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>1 charge related to Punishment for criminal trespass (IPC Section-447)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>1 charge related to Acts done by several persons in furtherance of common intention (IPC Section-34) <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_236453_1_7\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[7]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_236453_1_7\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/myneta.info\/loksabha2019\/candidate.php?candidate_id=11377\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">My Neta<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"AssetsProperties\"><\/span>Assets\/Properties<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Movable_Assets\"><\/span><strong>Movable Assets<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Cash: Rs. 59,353<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Deposits in Banks: Rs. 109000<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>LIC or other insurance Policies: Rs. 5,23,573<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Personal loans\/advance given: Rs. 13,62,500<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Jewellery: Rs. 1,65,000<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Other assets: Rs. 30,200 <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_236453_1_8\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[8]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_236453_1_8\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/myneta.info\/loksabha2019\/candidate.php?candidate_id=11377\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">My Neta<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Immovable_Assets\"><\/span><strong>Immovable Assets<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Agricultural Land: Rs. 21,00,000<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Non-Agricultural Land: Rs. 1,25,000<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Residential Buildings: Rs. 1,00,00,000<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Others: Rs. 75,000 <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_236453_1_9\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[9]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_236453_1_9\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/myneta.info\/loksabha2019\/candidate.php?candidate_id=11377\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">My Neta<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Net_Worth\"><\/span>Net Worth<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>In 2019, Subodh Kant Sahay&#8217;s net worth was calculated approximately at Rs. 1.23 crores. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_236453_1_10\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[10]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_236453_1_10\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/myneta.info\/loksabha2019\/candidate.php?candidate_id=11377\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">My Neta<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"FactsTrivia\"><\/span>Facts\/Trivia<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Renowned Janata Party politicians such as Chandrashekhar Singh, Satyendra Narayan Sinha, and Thakur Prasad were his mentors.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Subodh Kant Sahay referred to himself as a labourer from Bihar during a political rally in Ludhiana in 1991. He said,<br \/>\n<blockquote><p>I am one of the Bihari labourers come here to work your fields back to prosperity.\u201d<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_236528\" style=\"width: 437px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Sahay-campaigning-in-Ludhiana-in-1991.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-236528\" class=\"size-full wp-image-236528\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Sahay-campaigning-in-Ludhiana-in-1991.jpg\" alt=\"Sahay campaigning in Ludhiana in 1991\" width=\"427\" height=\"258\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Sahay-campaigning-in-Ludhiana-in-1991.jpg 427w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Sahay-campaigning-in-Ludhiana-in-1991-300x181.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 427px) 100vw, 427px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-236528\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sahay campaigning in Ludhiana in 1991<\/p><\/div><\/blockquote>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Former Indian Prime Minister <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/manmohan-singh\/\">Manmohan Singh<\/a> and former UPA Chairperson <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/sonia-gandhi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sonia Gandhi<\/a> used to praise him for his honesty and dedication during his tenure as a minister.\n<p><div id=\"attachment_236504\" style=\"width: 377px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-with-Manmohan-Singh-.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-236504\" class=\" wp-image-236504\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-with-Manmohan-Singh-.jpg\" alt=\"Subodh Kant Sahay with Manmohan Singh\" width=\"367\" height=\"426\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-with-Manmohan-Singh-.jpg 426w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-with-Manmohan-Singh--258x300.jpg 258w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 367px) 100vw, 367px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-236504\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Subodh Kant Sahay with Manmohan Singh<\/p><\/div><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>He often sets up events for young people at the national and state level. These events help and support uplifting the minorities and underprivileged.\n<p><div id=\"attachment_236509\" style=\"width: 474px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-while-addressing-the-problems-of-an-underprivileged-woman.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-236509\" class=\" wp-image-236509\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-while-addressing-the-problems-of-an-underprivileged-woman.jpg\" alt=\"Subodh Kant Sahay while addressing the problems of an underprivileged woman\" width=\"464\" height=\"315\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-while-addressing-the-problems-of-an-underprivileged-woman.jpg 541w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Subodh-Kant-Sahay-while-addressing-the-problems-of-an-underprivileged-woman-300x204.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 464px) 100vw, 464px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-236509\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Subodh Kant Sahay while addressing the problems of an underprivileged woman<\/p><\/div><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Subodh Kant Sahay enjoys eating poita-bhaat (fermented rice) and biscuits. During his free time, he loves to travel to faraway places and read books.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>In 2024, he accused the BJP of destroying the country&#8217;s federal structure after the arrest of Jharkhand Chief Minister <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/hemant-soren\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hemant Soren<\/a>. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_236453_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_236453_1_11\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[11]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_236453_1_11\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/zeenews.india.com\/hindi\/india\/delhi-ncr-haryana\/video\/hemant-soren-arrest-congress-leader-subodh-kant-sahay-says-bjp-destroyed-country-federal-structure\/2088251\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Zee News<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div class=\"489bcfb86580b123547338c91db0eff2\" data-index=\"3\" style=\"float: none; margin:3px 0 3px 0; text-align:center;\">\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\"\r\n     style=\"display:block\"\r\n     data-ad-format=\"autorelaxed\"\r\n     data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6769524711517462\"\r\n     data-ad-slot=\"2473600074\"><\/ins>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size: 0px; height: 0px; line-height: 0px; margin: 0; padding: 0; clear: both;\"><\/div><div class=\"speaker-mute footnotes_reference_container\"> <div class=\"footnote_container_prepare\"><p><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"footnotes_container_label_expand_236453_1\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_label pointer\" on=\"tap:footnote_references_cont